<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      background-color: #111827;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background-color: #1f2937;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 40px;
      border: 1px solid #374151;
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo img {
      height: 48px;
      width: auto;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #10b981;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }
    .features {
      background-color: #111827;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .features ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }
    .features li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .features li::marker {
      color: #10b981;
    }
    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #10b981;
      color: #111827 !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #374151;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #10b981;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="https://devometric.com/logo.png" alt="Devometric">
      </div>

      <h1>Welcome to Devometric!</h1>

      <p class="highlight">You're officially on the waitlist.</p>

      <p>Thank you for your interest in Devometric - the AI adoption coach for engineering teams. We're building something special to help teams like yours measure and improve their AI skills.</p>

      <div class="features">
        <p class="highlight" style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>What you'll get access to:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>AI Nativeness scoring for your team</li>
          <li>Personalized coaching and learning paths</li>
          <li>Latest AI trends and tool recommendations</li>
          <li>Team progress tracking and analytics</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>We'll notify you as soon as we're ready to welcome you aboard. In the meantime, feel free to explore our demo.</p>

      <div class="cta">
        <a href="https://devometric.com/demo" class="button">Try the Demo</a>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Questions? Reply to this email or reach out at <a href="mailto:risto@viher.it">risto@viher.it</a></p>
        <p style="margin-top: 12px;">Built by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rholappa/">Risto Holappa</a> at <a href="https://viher.it">Viher IT</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
